format: This data frame contains the following columns:
reference:
Milicer, H. and Szczotka, F. (1966) Age at Menarche in Warsaw girls in
1965.
Human Biology 38, 199–203.
description:
Description
Proportions of female children at various ages during adolescence
who have reached menarche.
title: Age of Menarche in Warsaw

parameters.Total: Total number of children in the group.
parameters.Age: Average age of the group.  (The groups are reasonably age homogeneous.)
